				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "**A Guest User, (non loged in visitor) Visits Web Site and Makes a Donation/Purchase**"
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-05-02T11:06:53.21538-04:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-05-02T12:12:50.152912-04:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "JdioudGKRLe5Z/CHDPXLNg=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "When someone visits the SEAS web site they are a 'guest'/'visitor'. They can browse the entire site and can also start a 'shopping session' where they can purchase one or all items. Currently examples of these items are  1) a membership, 2) a small boat day pass, or 3) a Basic Sailing course.\n\nAt checkout they must login to complete the purchase. If they are not a registered user then they just login. Otherwise they must set themselves up as a registered user."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
