				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "The guest user, they are not logged in, clicks on the login button. They are then shown a form where they can:\n1) Enter their user name and password and click on the  'Log In' button.\n2) Enter theur user name and click on the 'forgot username/password' button. (See Forgot Password story')."
